Package application

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Activity
    This class creates the type Activity for TableView activityTable in activity log screen: ActivityLog.fxml.
    ActivityController
    This class is the controller of the activity log screen: ActivityLog.fxml for manager.
    EditMenuController
    This class is the controller of the edit menu screen: EditMenu.fxml.
    GetTime
    This class get current date and time for this app in format "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss".
    LoginController
    This class is the controller of the first login screens: Login.fxml.
    Main
    This application runs a restaurant billing management system providing functions including: 1.
    MainController
    This class is the controller of the home screens after login screen: AdmiIn.fxml and StaffIn.fxml for manager and staff respectively, give access to all functions of the app.
    Menu
    This class creates the type Menu for TableView menuTable, TableView currentTable in home screen of manager:AdmiIn.fxml and home screen of staff:StaffIn.fxml; and for TableView editMenuTable in edit menu screen: EditMenu.fxml.
    Order
    This class creates the type Order for TableView searchResult in order list search screen: Search.fxml and StaffSearch.fxml.
    SearchController
    This class is the controller of the order list search screen for manager: Search.fxml and for staff: StaffSearch.fxml Can search the orders based on table number, dates and times intervals and ordered food.
    SQLiteConnection
    This class contains all methods that communicate with the database and a connection method.
    Staff
    This class creates the type Staff for TableView staffTable in edit staff account screen: EditStaff.fxml.
    StaffController
    This class is the controller of the edit staff screen: EditStaff.fxml.
    StringTo
    This class gives a method to convert a time string into a Timestamp.
